What is FASIDS?
Fire Ant Spatial Information and Decision Support aims
to:
1. create a knowledgebase to ease control of Red Imported Fire Ant
(RIFA) across Texas.
2. capture statewide data about distribution, abundance, and
treatment of RIFA impacts.
3. encourage individuals and organizations facing RIFA
management issue to share the information in a way that
benefits all RIFA stakeholders
